      "text": "The production of more and more manufacturing knowledge is no longer illicit [[Curiosity]] (curiositas), but at the same time admiration of creation and worship of God. But this reference to the super agent God is only a justification. It might satisfy theologians and keep them from intervening; but it reveals nothing about the structure of this theory, nothing about the meaning of its \"just so\", nothing about the advantage of this detour from making to knowing.\n"
